{"id":238338,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-四川访民何云华上访被关精神病院等迫害/","date":"2012-07-07T14:16:09Z","modified":"2012-07-07T14:16:09Z","title":"维权网 | 四川访民何云华上访被关精神病院等迫害（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>维权网信息员关小令报道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)7<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>6<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">上午</span>, </span><span>家住四川省广安市武胜县胜利镇金竹村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>社访民何云华老人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>向本网信息员诉说了他儿子在学校被人报复投毒死亡</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>公安机关包庇杀人凶手不立案</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>他被迫上访遭政府公安关精神病院打毒针迫害的事实。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据访民何云华讲述</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>他儿子何辉是于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日中午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>在桥亭乡中学吃午饭时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>被人在饭中下毒鼠强药毒杀身亡</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>案发后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>经广安市公安局于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>作出的刑事技术鉴定书认定</span><span> </span><span>“在何辉的胃组织及胃内容物中检出有鼠药毒鼠强。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>一个在校就餐的中学生</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>被人投毒身亡</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>至今得不到公安机关的立案。如此重大、社会反响强烈的投毒杀人案，武胜县公安局却不及时破案，该局刑警大队大队长李斌，却带着手下警员对死者家属实施抢劫，非法抢走何云华现金</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>万元，何云华气愤地说，在这警匪横行下，我上访到省里无人理，上访北京被绑架关精神病院强行吃毒药，打毒针残酷迫害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，在武胜县公安局领导李斌，武胜县胜利镇党委书记华晓泉，镇长李荣峰的组织下，将有冤无处申的访民何云华强行绑架送进南充市精神病院，指使主管医生袁纯孝，非法使用暴力捆绑何云华，强行灌食毒药和打毒针摧残至何云华生命垂危时，已关押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">136</span><span>天的何云华才放出精神病院。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民何云华在关南充市精神病院期间</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>南充市精神病院主治医师袁化孝于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>，给何云华的诊断结论是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、精神分裂症；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、糖尿病。建议：未治愈，需继续用抗精神病药物治疗。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民何云华的亲属强烈抗议政府和南充市精神病医院联手报复残害何云华，要求将何云华转往射洪县精神病医院诊治，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>，经射洪县精神病医院专家会诊，何云华鉴定为“精神功能正常”，</span><span> </span><span>目前未发现任何精神病症状。情况属实，将此证明。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>由此看出两个完全相反的病情诊断结论，谁是谁非，大家一目了然。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民何云华说，像这样被政府非法关押精神病院，关黑监狱殴打、恐吓的报复手段</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多次。生命安全已直接受到严重威胁，长期漂泊北京不敢回家，何云华老人悲叹道：我儿冤未申，真是死又不甘，活着又无路可走，真不知中国这个社会到何时才能见光明。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-jeqnnH59Fpg/T_gJJe3qvxI/AAAAAAAAJCE/t5XoXGINOBY/s1600/%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E4%BD%95%E4%BA%91%E5%8D%8E.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-jeqnnH59Fpg/T_gJJe3qvxI/AAAAAAAAJCE/t5XoXGINOBY/s320/%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E4%BD%95%E4%BA%91%E5%8D%8E.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-eRQX_0s7F3A/T_gJZGutorI/AAAAAAAAJCM/qz4rSxAR7aY/s1600/DSCF5985.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-eRQX_0s7F3A/T_gJZGutorI/AAAAAAAAJCM/qz4rSxAR7aY/s320/DSCF5985.JPG\" width=\"227\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-6IL2jDjAh0Y/T_gJfiexLBI/AAAAAAAAJCU/q2wCGCY6yls/s1600/%E6%B3%95%E5%8C%BB%E9%89%B4%E5%AE%9A.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"239\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-6IL2jDjAh0Y/T_gJfiexLBI/AAAAAAAAJCU/q2wCGCY6yls/s320/%E6%B3%95%E5%8C%BB%E9%89%B4%E5%AE%9A.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5285077257247167906?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/f6e23a7891E58D8E.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}